At the 250,000/500,000/50,000 level, English (17.6m) min-raised on the button. A call from Julius (39m) landed a flop where Julius check-called 1.111 million to see the turn. It was more of the same for Julius who check-called 2.777 million. When the hit the river, Julius checked to English who shoved for abut 12.7 million.
